data.description:
Custom home built by John Schedcik in 2022 on pier and slab foundation - this uniquely design traditional 2x6 built home with 6 inch of foam encapsulation insulation - has all the charm and class with its 3 bedrooms, 2 baths plus office!
Oak hardwood floors through the entire home and a beautiful upgraded kitchen with oversized 9x5 island, storage galore and covered in natural quartz counters throughout the home.

Primary suite with catwalk balcony overlooking living room with vaulted ceilings and exquisite freestanding cast iron fireplace.
Detached garage with 18x8 and 12x12 doors - rv stall or mechanic bay would accommodate a lift. 30 and 50amp plugs as well as water and septic hookup in garage - couple be converted to mother-in-law suite.
5 acres fenced in 6 strand electric and cross fenced behind the house. Power and water to outbuilding as well as 200 amp panel in house and shop.
